video.title: Z Nation
video.synopsis: A team embarks on a perilous cross-country mission to transport the one man who survived a deadly zombie virus, hoping he holds the key to a vaccine.

episodes.synopsis: A team of everyday heroes transports the only known survivor of a zombie virus from New York to California in hopes of using his blood for a vaccine.
episodes.title: Puppies and Kittens

episodes.synopsis: In need of gas, the team follows a suspicious stranger to a damaged oil refinery deep inside a New Jersey zone packed with zombies.
episodes.title: Fracking Zombies

episodes.synopsis: Out for revenge on Cassandra, her dangerous former "family" catches up with the team and kidnaps Addy, endangering the mission.
episodes.title: Philly Feast

episodes.synopsis: Citizen Z directs the team to a helicopter controlled by a mysterious general living atop a heavily guarded skyscraper where zombies roam freely.
episodes.title: Full Metal Zombie

episodes.synopsis: A tornado forces the team to Warren's hometown, where she searches for her husband, whom she lost in the early days of the apocalypse.
episodes.title: Home Sweet Zombie

episodes.synopsis: After taking refuge in a safe enclave where no weapons are allowed, the team battles for control of the compound against a zombie-worshipping cult.
episodes.title: Resurrection Z

episodes.synopsis: Lost and out of water in rural Kansas, the team is on the verge of breaking up when they arrive at a crazy gun show and Wild West bar.
episodes.title: Welcome to the Fu-Bar

episodes.synopsis: When the last surviving cosmonaut from the International Space Station crashes to Earth, Citizen Z gets a new friend, who may have a secret agenda.
episodes.title: Zunami

episodes.synopsis: Mack and Addy become trapped by a zombie they just can't kill. A series of escalating fights with the zombie forces them to confront an ugly truth.
episodes.title: Die Zombie Die... Again

episodes.synopsis: While in South Dakota, an imminent meltdown forces the team to help the locals repair a nearby nuclear power plant full of radiated zombies.
episodes.title: Going Nuclear

episodes.synopsis: In need of shelter and medical supplies, the team seeks refuge in an all-female compound where men are not allowed.
episodes.title: Sisters of Mercy

episodes.synopsis: Three strangers earn their way on the team, taking a keen interest in Murphy, which eventually takes a deadly turn.
episodes.title: Murphy's Law

episodes.synopsis: The team is rerouted to a lab located in an abandoned missile silo, where they search for the developer of the experimental vaccine given to Murphy.
episodes.title: Doctor of the Dead

episodes.synopsis: Moments after the nuclear weapons launch, the group splits up to outrun the blast and Citizen Z offers a bounty for Murphy and his vaccine-rich blood.
episodes.title: The Murphy

episodes.synopsis: The bounty placed on Murphy's head by Citizen Z is irresistible to everyone. The team is reunited but now must fight both zombies and bounty hunters.
episodes.title: White Light

episodes.synopsis: After hitching a ride with a caravan of nuclear blast survivors, the group is attacked by a new strain of superfast zombies.
episodes.title: Zombie Road

episodes.synopsis: Murphy and Cassandra reach a greenhouse growing Batch 47, rumored to be a natural cure for the zombie virus, but it's guarded by fearsome hybrids.
episodes.title: Batch 47

episodes.synopsis: A face from the past returns with a big surprise for Murphy. Meanwhile, the group faces a new deadly threat at a Mennonite farm.
episodes.title: Zombaby!

episodes.synopsis: Murphy is bewitched by his baby daughter, but the team worries there's more to her than meets the eye. Vasquez sneaks away for a secret meeting.
episodes.title: Zombie Baby Daddy

episodes.synopsis: After an accident splits up the group, 10K finds himself in the company of two shady characters who put his life in danger.
episodes.title: Down the Mississippi

episodes.synopsis: As the team searches frantically for Murphy, he falls into a trap set by an overzealous zombie fan and engages in a battle of wits with his captor.
episodes.title: The Collector

episodes.synopsis: Strange lights and a mysterious woman lead the team on an adventure through an abandoned New Mexico Air Force base in search of zombie aliens.
episodes.title: RoZwell

episodes.synopsis: When a horde of zombies drives them onto sacred Native American land, the group finds two halves of a tribe using different strategies to survive.
episodes.title: We Were Nowhere Near the Grand Canyon

episodes.synopsis: Taking shelter at a hotel run by white-collar survivors, the group gets mired in corporate politics -- until gunfire shakes up the agenda.
episodes.title: Corporate Retreat

episodes.synopsis: The Queen of the Zeros issues an invitation to the team as Dr. Kurian prepares to test his new vaccine and Vasquez decides his moment has come.
episodes.title: Party With the Zeros

episodes.synopsis: Chaos erupts when Dr. Kurian's vaccine has unintended effects. Murphy uses his powers of mental manipulation to alter the chain of command.
episodes.title: Adios Muchachos

episodes.synopsis: As they finally cross the border into California, the members of the team reflect on how far they've come since the zombie apocalypse began.
episodes.title: Day One

episodes.synopsis: A journey through the abandoned streets of LA leads the team toward a mobile CDC lab, but the Zeros are hot on their heels.
episodes.title: End Times

episodes.synopsis: In a flashback, the survivors are led to a mysterious compound and lab occupied by residents living in fear of The Man, a villain with a dreaded list.
episodes.title: No Mercy Part 1; No Mercy Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Competing groups scramble to retrieve an off-target airdrop, including the heroes, Murphy with his new Blends, Pan Asian soldiers and zombies.
episodes.title: A New Mission

episodes.synopsis: Warren and the others follow a survivor who draws peculiar zombie interest, while Murphy saves a dying girl and Citizen Z leaves the Inuit village.
episodes.title: Murphy's Miracle

episodes.synopsis: Warren and the others get caught in a battle fought by vigilantes, while Dr. Merch formulates a booster shot for Murphy with unexpected results.
episodes.title: Escorpion and the Red Hand

episodes.synopsis: While Murphy reviews Dr. Merch's complex notes, an injured and ailing 10K escapes from a Blend, only to be pursued by a pack of zombie wolves.
episodes.title: Little Red and the WolfZ

episodes.synopsis: Imprisoned by a psychotic nurse, Doc discovers 10K in the same predicament (and awaiting a lobotomy), leading to a desperate bid to escape.
episodes.title: Doc Flew over the Cuckoo's Nest

episodes.synopsis: 10K returns to the group, revealing Murphy's swelling ranks and secret mission, while The Man tries to kidnap Murphy but underestimates his followers.
episodes.title: Welcome to Murphytown

episodes.synopsis: En route to Illinois, Doc and Addy encounter Sketchy and Skeezy on the "campaign trail," then try to diagnose a mysterious illness in South Dakota.
episodes.title: Election Day

episodes.synopsis: Warren acknowledges that Murphy must be stopped and embarks on a quest to enlist the elusive Red Hand in extracting him.
episodes.title: Heart of Darkness

episodes.synopsis: Doc and Addy try to persuade Lucy's family to leave with them, while 10K's loyalty is tested when he returns to Murphy.
episodes.title: They Grow Up So Quickly

episodes.synopsis: Seeking a way to notify Warren about recent developments, Doc spends the night with three women who have a radio tower in their castle-style compound.
episodes.title: Doc's Angels

episodes.synopsis: While 10K struggles against his captor, the attack on Murphytown begins with help from the Red Hand, leading to a faceoff between Murphy and Warren.
episodes.title: The Siege of Murphytown

episodes.synopsis: Addy pursues Lucy despite everything The Man can throw at her, Lucy creates obstacles for her kidnapper, and an Addy-Doc reunion looms.
episodes.title: Duel

episodes.synopsis: Addy and Doc encounter an unusual zombie, then reunite with Warren and the rest of the group, launching a final assault to save Lucy from The Man.
episodes.title: Everybody Dies in the End

episodes.synopsis: Plagued by eerie visions after waking from a coma, Warren quickly grows uneasy inside Zona, and not just because its denizens hail Murphy as a hero.
episodes.title: Warren's Dream

episodes.synopsis: Zona spirals into chaos as the residents suddenly turn bloodthirsty. In the outside world, the rest of the team gets stuck in a gunfight.
episodes.title: Escape from Zona

episodes.synopsis: After escaping from Zona, Warren and Murphy reunite with what's left of the gang, including Lucy, who's not all that thrilled to see her dad.
episodes.title: The Vanishing

episodes.synopsis: With Warren in the lead, the group heads east into a vehicular graveyard, with a reluctant Murphy in tow. Meanwhile, Lucy's frustrations boil over.
episodes.title: A New Mission: Keep Moving

episodes.synopsis: Kidnapped by an unseen force, the team winds up trapped in a labyrinthine underground lair, where survival depends on successfully completing tasks.
episodes.title: The Unknowns

episodes.synopsis: Lucy takes decisive action as Murphy begins to succumb to a zombie bite, while Warren's visions of the black rainbow grow clearer and more insistent.
episodes.title: Back from the Undead

episodes.synopsis: Warren and friends encounter the last thing they need while reeling from a devastating loss: killer clowns running a carnival from hell.
episodes.title: Warren's Wedding

episodes.synopsis: Holed up in a church at the Canadian border, the group fends off Zs and meets a mysterious stranger, who helps a questioning Warren make a decision.
episodes.title: Crisis of Faith

episodes.synopsis: Seeking a way to communicate with Kaya, the team finds an abandoned TV news station, one that reported on the dawning zombie apocalypse live on air.
episodes.title: We Interupt This Program

episodes.synopsis: Murphy and Doc run into some old acquaintances when they seek refuge inside a barbershop, a reunion that soon turns into a close shave for everyone.
episodes.title: Frenemies

episodes.synopsis: The team follows Warren south based on her visions, ending up at the body-strewn Mercy Labs. Up north, Kaya and Simon uncover clues to Black Rainbow.
episodes.title: Return to Mercy Labs

episodes.synopsis: In their bid to stop Black Rainbow, the team goes in search of the president's thumbs. Not surprisingly, the mission doesn't quite go as planned.
episodes.title: Mt. Weather

episodes.synopsis: Will this be the end of everything? The gang arrives at their final destination, where Warren learns what and who propelled her vision quest.
episodes.title: The Black Rainbow

episodes.synopsis: An injured Warren gets a helping hand from a mysterious man. Meanwhile, the rest of the gang notices some odd happenings on their way to NewMerica.
episodes.title: Welcome to the Newpocalypse

episodes.synopsis: Warren's seemingly idyllic new life takes a turn when Murphy meets her rescuer. Back in Altura, democracy comes to the apocalypse as the polls open.
episodes.title: A New Life

episodes.synopsis: The dream of a united society of humans and talkers suffers a catastrophic blow as dissension grows, with the gang caught up in the chaos.
episodes.title: Escape from Altura

episodes.synopsis: On the hunt for Lt. Dante after the attack, Warren, Doc, Citizen Z and George head to Pacifica, where they find tempers flaring and trouble brewing.
episodes.title: Pacifica

episodes.synopsis: George's hope of forming a strong, unified country dims after another bombing. Back in Altura, 10K tries to come to grips with his new reality.
episodes.title: Killing All the Books

episodes.synopsis: Determined to find Dante and get to the bottom of the bombings, Warren, George and Doc wind up inside a den of iniquity run by a very familiar face.
episodes.title: Limbo

episodes.synopsis: While Doc and George embark on an American history-packed trip to Altura, Warren and Murphy lead the rest of the gang to the rumored bizkit bakery.
episodes.title: Doc's Stoned History

episodes.synopsis: To find out who's cutting off the bizkit supply to the talkers, Warren and the gang decide to check out the farm producing the flour.
episodes.title: Heartland

episodes.synopsis: An unexpected reunion takes place when the gang sets out to learn why much-needed water from a dam has stopped flowing.
episodes.title: The Water Keepers

episodes.synopsis: The discovery of a hazardous garbage dump manned by enslaved talkers moves the gang one step closer to figuring out the secret ingredient in bizkits.
episodes.title: State of Mine

episodes.synopsis: Now that they know who's behind the bizkit scheme, Warren and the gang need information, so they make a deal with a group of hackers.
episodes.title: Hackerville

episodes.synopsis: As Altura's election day approaches, anyone not deemed worthy of citizenship is in danger, so the gang enacts a risky plan to ensure justice for all.
episodes.title: At All Cost

episodes.synopsis: It's time to vote, and the fate of the future comes down to this. As the gang sets their endgame in motion, secrets are revealed -- and answers found.
episodes.title: The End of Everything
